longBusinessSummary: Sveafastigheter AB (publ), a real estate company, owns, builds, and manages residential properties in Sweden. The company operates in Property Management and New Construction segments. It also develops and manages rental apartments and condominiums. In addition, it engages in the project development and building rights activities. The company was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Sveafastigheter AB (publ) is a subsidiary of SBB i Norden AB (publ).
